<item>
            <title>[HADOOP-8314] HttpServer#hasAdminAccess should return false if authorization is enabled but user is not authenticated</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HADOOP-8314</link>
                <project id="12310240" key="HADOOP">Hadoop Common</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If the user is not authenticated (request.getRemoteUser() returns NULL) or there is not authentication filter configured (thus returning also NULL), hasAdminAccess should return false. Note that a filter could allow anonymous access, thus the first case.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
