&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;+      response.sendError(HttpServletResponse.SC_UNAUTHORIZED,
+                         &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;Unauthenticated users are not &quot;&lt;/span&gt; +
+                         &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;unauthorized to access &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;this&lt;/span&gt; page.&quot;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Otherwise the patch looks good. +1 pending Jenkins.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
